          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10132,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1013201,
            "DisplayOrder": 400,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10100,
            "LocalizeKR": "……어라? 선생님은,\n어떻게 건너편에……? ",
            "LocalizeJP": "……あれ？\n先生は、どうやって\n向こう側に……？",
